FIGURES 61–68. 
<taxonomicName box="[347,615,1738,1760]" class="Insecta" family="Micropezidae" genus="Paramimegralla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stiltoides" status="new species">
